window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>My fate has never been my own.</p> <p>Nia:</p> <p>Declared savior of all werewolves when I was born, I never had a chance at a normal life. I didn’t get parents and I’ve been unable to leave my wolf pack’s territory for 22 years. If a hunter finds me, I risk more than my own life. I risk my pack.</p> <p>I’ve kept myself busy training, learning to fight, sculpting my body into a weapon I can use to defend myself when the hunters come for me.</p> <p>And they will.</p> <p>They’re looking for me.</p> <p>But then he shows up.</p> <p>Suddenly, I want things I’m not allowed to have...</p> <p>Bruno:</p> <p>My trip to visit the Rocky Mountain Pack alpha was supposed to be quick. In and out.</p> <p>Then I see her.</p> <p>And she’s...everything she’s not supposed to be.</p> <p>Everything I’m not supposed to want.</p> <p>I can’t take my eyes off her.</p> <p><b>Note: </b>The Rocky Mountain Pack series is gritty, sexy, and action-packed paranormal shifter romance. <i>Wolf Bonds</i> is a full-length novel recommended for mature listeners due to language, sexual situations, and graphic fighting scenes.</p>"; 
